<div class="marketing__section marketing__testimonials">
  <h2>How journalists are using Pro</h2>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="testimonials__grid">
      <div class="testimonials__item">
        <div class="testimonial__body">
          <a href="https://www.mysociety.org/2019/06/05/case-study-sold-from-under-you-by-the-bureau-of-investigative-journalism/">
          <%= image_tag("alaveteli-pro/promo-sold.jpg",
                        alt: _("Using WhatDoTheyKnow Pro to build a nationwide picture of the public properties being sold off by councils")) %>
          </a>

          <p><a href="https://www.mysociety.org/2019/06/05/case-study-sold-from-under-you-by-the-bureau-of-investigative-journalism/">Sold From Under You</a>  — the Bureau of investigative Journalism used Pro to send requests to councils up and down the county to build a nationwide picture of the public properties being sold off by councils in the face of austerity.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonials__item">
        <div class="testimonial__body">
          <a href="https://www.mysociety.org/2018/09/20/whatdotheyknow-pro-helps-set-the-news-agenda/">
          <%= image_tag("alaveteli-pro/promo-overspend.jpg",
                        alt: _("Bringing facts about campagin overspending to light with the embargo function")) %>
          </a>

          <p>Investigative journalist Jenna Corderoy has made good use of Pro’s Embargo function, keeping her extensive Brexit-related investigations private until her stories broke, bringing facts about <a href="https://www.mysociety.org/2018/09/20/whatdotheyknow-pro-helps-set-the-news-agenda/">campaign overspending</a> and <a href="https://www.mysociety.org/2019/07/05/whatdotheyknow-pro-helps-journalists-further-transparency-accountability-and-public-trust/">ERG</a> research to the public, among several other important stories.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <small class="image-credits">Image credits: <a href="https://unsplash.com/photos/4IZPCkTsBpY">Daniel von Appen</a>, <a href="https://unsplash.com/photos/_Zua2hyvTBk">Roman Kraft</a></small>
  </div>

  <div class="marketing__cta">
    <% if feature_enabled?(:pro_pricing) %>
    <%= link_to _('Plans and pricing'), pro_plans_path, class: "button" %>
    <% elsif feature_enabled?(:pro_self_serve) %>
      <%= render partial: 'self_serve_button' %>
    <% else %>
      <%= render partial: 'account_request_form' %>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
